-- CVC and Blackstone place 100 mln Merlin shares
-- 
-- Thu Jun 12, 2014 02:56PM EDT
-- None



June 12 (Reuters) - Merlin Entertainments' <MERL.L> private equity backers CVC Capital Partners Ltd [CVC.UL] and Blackstone Group LP <BX.N> are placing 100 million shares of the British theme park owner through Morgan Stanley and Deutsche Bank, the German lender said.

